flowchart TB

Member["Avenu Member<br>[Person]"]
Admin["Avenu Admin<br>[Person]"]

subgraph Avenu["Avenu Mail System"]

    Frontend["Frontend<br>[Container: React SPA]<br>Used by admins and members"]

    Backend["Backend<br>[Container: Python, Flask]<br>Owns business logic, persistence, notifications,<br>external integrations, and self-hosted OCR"]

    Scheduler["Scheduler<br>[Container: Python Job Runner]<br>Triggers scheduled jobs via backend APIs<br>(does not access DB directly)"]

    OCR["Self-hosted OCR<br>[Backend capability: Tesseract]<br>Extracts text from staged mail photos"]

end

subgraph External["External Systems"]

    MongoDB["MongoDB Atlas<br>[Managed Database]<br>System of record for users, teams, mailboxes,<br>mail entries, requests, and notification logs"]

    Optix["Optix API<br>[Identity Provider]<br>Authoritative source for users and companies"]

    EmailProvider["Email Provider API<br>[External Notification Provider]"]

    SMSProvider["SMS Provider API<br>[External Notification Provider]"]

end

Member -->|"Uses"| Frontend
Admin -->|"Uses"| Frontend

Frontend -->|"JSON/HTTPS API calls"| Backend
Scheduler -->|"Internal HTTP calls"| Backend

Backend -->|"Runs OCR locally"| OCR
Backend -->|"Reads/writes via TLS"| MongoDB
Backend -->|"Syncs identity"| Optix
Backend -->|"Sends email"| EmailProvider
Backend -->|"Sends SMS"| SMSProvider
